The Swallow’s Nest built by aerodramus swiftlets. The colours are ivory-white and white. A broken swallow’s nest is a shape birdnest that broken form of a whole swallow’s nest, it can also be called an angle if the fault is angular. But don’t worry, the nutritional value is still the same 🙂

The Value of NestOne Swallow’s Nest:

💯 Natural Processing

🤝 Direct from Our Birdnest House

❤️ High Technology Processing

Did You Know?
